r> zatim promijenite prijevod na bočnoj traci.','Don\'t forget to Save Translation. Use keyboard shortcut CTRL(⌘) + S'=>'Ne zaboravite spremiti prijevod. Koristite prečac na tipkovnici CTRL(⌘) + S','Switch language to see the translation changes directly on the page.'=>'Prebacite jezik da biste izravno vidjeli promjene u prijevodu na stranici.','Search for any text in this page in the dropdown.'=>'Pretražite bilo koji tekst na ovoj stranici u padajućem izborniku.','Your %s license has <span class="trp-license-status-emphasized">expired</span>.'=>'Vaša %s licencija je <span class="trp-license-status-emphasized">istekla</span>.','Please renew your license to continue receiving access to TranslatePress AI, premium addons, automatic updates and support.'=>'Obnovite svoju licencu kako biste nastavili primati pristup TranslatePress AI, premium dodacima, automatskim ažuriranjima i podršci.','Renew Now'=>'Obnovi sada','<strong>This Black Friday, renew your license at a special price</strong> to continue receiving access to product downloads, automatic updates, and support.'=>'<strong>Ovaj Crni petak, obnovite svoju licencu po posebnoj cijeni</strong> kako biste nastavili primati pristup preuzimanjima proizvoda, automatskim ažuriranjima i podršci.','Get Deal'=>'Uzmite ponudu','Your %s license was <span class="trp-license-status-emphasized">refunded</span>.'=>'Vaša %s licenca je <span class="trp-license-status-emphasized">refundirana</span>.','Please purchase a new license to continue receiving access to TranslatePress AI, premium addons, automatic updates and support.'=>'Kupite novu licencu kako biste nastavili primati pristup TranslatePress AI, premium dodacima, automatskim ažuriranjima i podršci.','Purchase a new license'=>'Kupite novu licencu','Your %s license is <span class="trp-license-status-emphasized">missing or invalid</span>.'=>'Vaša licenca <span class="trp-license-status-emphasized">nedostaje ili je nevažeća</span>%s.','Please enter a valid license to get access 